Notes: SP's sixth straight win...SP led by as many as 16 points at 61-45 with 11:34
left...Trailing 74-63 with 4:16 left, Stout went on 10-2 run to cut lead to
76-73 with 1:36 left...SP's Kraemer hit 4 of 6 free throws in final 1:18 for
career high 23 points...SP's Heuer scored of 15 of her 23 points in first half
Game.Officials: Lou Pitt,  Becky Blank,  Barb Fagan
